Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生氣的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於肯說話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在想要等到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不怎麼喝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服借一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直悶在房間裏好幾天沒洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是會介意這個的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長在錄音室等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝一罐啤酒又不用多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得冬彌君…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在車上喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我昨天…做了那樣的事  以為音樂節的事已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣就不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只能說明這就是此等程度的鬧劇而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀我們避免了時間的浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這是由綺的第一次的反抗  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這個進步  我想坦率地高興一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到想給獎勵的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼理奈不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加愚蠢的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈是我的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺是除此以外的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來  由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你介紹下你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是絕對的秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那一天  從那一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集畫成為了目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拜託長瀨幫我收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了很多人力  時間和金錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  看上去每幅畫都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而沒有一幅是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是贗品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在倫敦看到的不是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在這一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在尋找著那僅此一幅的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈她沒有能成為真品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺  現在的你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些畫都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來由綺有看畫的眼光…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說這只是視力的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確這些並不是完全一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是人類畫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然對畫不怎麼瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這些畫裏的人都不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼  由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方先生才是  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戲弄我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說點什麼吧  弗蘭奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你是經紀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演員開這麼差勁的玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  弗蘭奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  還拿別的畫來欺騙我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去  由綺你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該…說出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺小姐  國王可能是赤裸著身體的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把工作當什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是毫無辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾會覺得理奈是個房間裏的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆當成是幅畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小英居然有這樣的嗜好  真是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪裏知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一幅畫想讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是鑒賞家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個女孩呢  還有百合花來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花開得很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者叫傑弗裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認識作者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年後想再見一次  而畫卻不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未忘記…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你願意讓給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能免費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開價吧  要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  來場遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候已經…我的命運已盡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成為我的夥伴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  你看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以少女為主題的印象畫展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  來這邊把衣服脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是不是依靠感官的外行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是聽從我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你趴在地下舔我鞋子也行  沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快點脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像狗一樣趴在這裏舔我的腳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都聽我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  給你寫一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不滿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來嘲笑我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓還什麼都不懂的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來對我阿諛奉承
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由綺小姐的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是由綺的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從找到由綺  一切都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都變得不合拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:12:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不正好說明了由綺小姐存在的重要性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個習慣不會有什麼好處的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從由綺小姐身上感受到了這麼大的壓力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是來嘲笑我的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把畫全部都看成一樣的也不能怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺一切都是假的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽長瀨先生一再的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能一味地收購也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為您已經記不得在倫敦親眼見過的那幅真品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然心裏明白  但卻不想承認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信拯救了自己的那幅畫竟然被忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信這次的才是真品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜連理奈小姐都賣掉換來的那個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也應該明白了  只是不去正視
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這個好機會醒過來如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想理奈小姐的代價絕對不小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子就不用了  我不是歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭奇  過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情和你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那些討人厭的畫都趕緊處理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要住在這裏  有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不好呢  在夜裏吃甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  白天抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來探病了？  聽老爸說的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天跟理奈第一次出勤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我緊張得不得了  理奈她還是平時的理奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼凜然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和瑪瑙是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只見過一次  在由綺…森川由綺的演唱會上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  對了  還負責過森川由綺麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  是由綺的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不太好吧  說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  沒什麼好隱瞞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我這隨便亂猜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是因為這個才說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的日程安排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不一件件看也要記住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就去被藤井冬彌先生包下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方理奈獨唱演唱會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼…  真過分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事找學生處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才美笑和彰也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去  雖然我想這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然彰他們也在的話就久違地大家一起去吃頓飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來還有個地方要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和麻奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和麻奈和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒吵過架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上要考試了吧  我想總是把她帶出來也不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是藤井…先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是山本  學生處的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼怎麼樣呢  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠嗆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再給你介紹個其他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  兼職的話現在有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:17:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  我還在繼續做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是給我介紹了一份好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被叫做女神  鼓勵了我  我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏我都不知道該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  我只是想道聲謝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很討厭吧  和我這樣的大媽一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天開始了時間不規則的打工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候都可以  因為很閒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的話倒是有空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？  接下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太突然也不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  去嗎  接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃什麼  我知道一家有好吃的法國料理的店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都好哪兒都好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.27,0:18:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為你陪我的謝禮  告訴你一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  觀月小姐的家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙  又…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個人不是學生處的職員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都可以…  只是在喝茶而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊  從以前起就對那傢伙的性格…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是遙的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是理奈小姐吧  由綺的前輩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  緒方理奈和冬彌喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  和我的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不好哦  吃醋可不像彰君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像田丸一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道田丸君的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他變成那樣的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他其實不是那麼壞的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  美笑只是把他甩了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  只是甩了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  好像變得消沉起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說觀月小姐的媽媽是演藝事務所的社長就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  為什麼連名字都改了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對女兒周圍的人啊  業界啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去一下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為必須要打個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井先生才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的消遣的道具？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學的學生處的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已經不需要我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個詞我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再和其他的女性一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所管不到的障礙物有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天森川由綺小姐就正式從流行歌曲工作室畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺今天不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有義務告訴他社員工演員的日程安排
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十一頁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.93,0:24:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要回到岔路口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.66,0:24:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果選右邊就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.99,0:24:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿了後悔的路程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.59,0:24:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

